== README

This is a rails 4 app that use the gem 'fullcalendar-rails' to create a calendar that organize events and for authentication gem 'devise'..

The app provides a calendar for every user where the users can record their events.
The events are saved in a mysql database.
User B can't see User A events..

Ruby version: 2.1.2

Rails version: 4.1.4

Database engine: Mysql


